title: Green Mountain
description: Vegetarian Restaurant in a spacious and clean setting. Features Chinese, Indonesian, Thai, and Malay style dishes.  Picture menu with English names for some dishes. No English spoken. Directions: When traveling south on Min Hang road towards the airport, Guan Pei road is the final street on the right before you reach Guang Shang South road. Chinese Name: 高山青素食餐厅 Chinese Address: 昆明市民航路红星酒店旁关培路7号（官渡区农业局对面）.
streetAddress: 7 Guan Pei Road, Guan Shang, Yunnan
